  "book.netherman.page1.line1": "Welcome to §4§lCult of Azazel§f§l mod!",
  "book.netherman.page1.line2": "Here's a quick guide to what's in the mod.",
  "book.netherman.page1.line3": "Thanks for the play!",
  "book.netherman.page1.line4": "Author: §4Benj1kus",
  "book.netherman.page1.line5": "§c§lDESCRIPTION:",
  "book.netherman.page1.line6": "The mod adds new structures to the game,",
  "book.netherman.page1.line7": "The mod is primarily focused on the Nether dimension.",

  "book.netherman.page2.line1": "§c§lSTRUCTURES: §4§lNether mansion",
  "book.netherman.page2.line2": "It's a huge mansion divided into 3 zones:",
  "book.netherman.page2.line3": "§6§lTHE CURSED QUARRIES",
  "book.netherman.page2.line4": "§с§lTHE SACRED CITY",
  "book.netherman.page2.line5": "§4§lAZAZEL'S LAIR",
  "book.netherman.page2.line6": "§6§lTHE CURSED QUARRIES:§f§l The start area",
  "book.netherman.page2.line7": "where player will encounter the §4Manipulators.",
  "book.netherman.page2.line8": "By defeating them, player can free villagers",
  "book.netherman.page2.line9": "and get a reward.",

  "book.netherman.page3.line1": "§с§lTHE SACRED CITY:§f§l Area 2",
  "book.netherman.page3.line2": "This is primarily an exploration area.",
  "book.netherman.page3.line3": "You can find 2 NPCs:",
  "book.netherman.page3.line4": "§сDoctor§f§l - can give out random potions",
  "book.netherman.page3.line5": "§сBlacksmith§f§l - can disassemble tools and repair them",
  "book.netherman.page3.line6": "without removing their enchantments.",
  "book.netherman.page3.line7": "§4§lAZAZEL'S LAIR:§f§l Final area",
  "book.netherman.page3.line8": "Inside the barrel you'll find instruction",
  "book.netherman.page3.line9": "explaining how to summon §4§lAZAZEL.",

  "book.netherman.page4.line1": "§с§lMinor structures in Nether",
  "book.netherman.page4.line2": "§2§lOverworld Structures",
  "book.netherman.page4.line3": "Find the pipes. There are cracks underneath them.3 times ",
  "book.netherman.page4.line4": "Compass.Pillar.Head.Puzzle.Hints Inside.",
  "book.netherman.page4.line5": "Maze.Caution.Up",
  "book.netherman.page4.line6": "God?",
  "book.netherman.page4.line7": "2 ways.Cult way-quests.Time 3 days",

  "book.netherman.page5.line1": "§с§lMOBS: §4Ghastly",
  "book.netherman.page5.line2": "can make hive out of Crimson stem,",
  "book.netherman.page5.line3": "can make crimson honey,",
  "book.netherman.page5.line4": "can be tamed,",
  "book.netherman.page5.line5": "can show the way to Nether mansion.",
  "book.netherman.page5.line6": "§с§lMinor mobs:",
  "book.netherman.page5.line7": "§6Welcomer§f§l - greets player at the entrance.",
  "book.netherman.page5.line8": "§6Trader§f§l - offers variety of trades.",
  "book.netherman.page5.line9": "§6Gilded golem§f§l - protects believers, absorbs items and blood.",
  "book.netherman.page5.line10": "§4Gehinnom§f§l - guard, best not to provoke.",
  "book.netherman.page5.line11": "§4Manipulator§f§l - servant of Azazel, handles resources.",

  "book.netherman.page6.line1": "§с§lITEMS",
  "book.netherman.page6.line2": "§сTotem of rebirth:",
  "book.netherman.page6.line3": "When the player takes fatal damage, it teleports to spawnpoint.",
  "book.netherman.page6.line4": "§4Manipulation Staff:",
  "book.netherman.page6.line5": "Allows you to apply Manipulation effect,",
  "book.netherman.page6.line6": "pull entities and summon wither skeletons.",
  "book.netherman.page6.line7": "§e§lTHANKS FOR PLAYING!",
  "book.netherman.page6.line8": "Author: §4Benj1kus",


